locality: [1914DA] Grid ref. Regio Kunene. Opuwo District, 14 km W of Kamanjab on road to Grootberg.
Along Singida-Babati rd, 9.5 km from Hanang Dist boundary. SW end of Masware mbuga. Flat valley bottom, seasonally flooded black clay. Herb meadow dominated by annuals.

14 km on Sepuka rd W from Singida. NW end of Ititi Swamp, heavy black clay. Open bushland of Acacia drepanolobium mostly 3-6m high, also Balanites & Albizia. Ground layer dominated by Justicia betonica.
at Godjeb farm of Catholic mission, between Jimma and Bonga.
